tle, new.body);\n    END\n  `);\n\n  return db;","originalFile":"import Database from 'better-sqlite3';\n\nexport function createDatabase(path?: string): Database.Database {\n  const db = path ? new Database(path) : new Database(':memory:');\n\n  db.pragma('journal_mode = WAL');\n  db.pragma('foreign_keys = ON');\n\n  // Create notes table\n  db.exec(`\n    CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS notes (\n      id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n      title TEXT NOT NULL,\n      body TEXT NOT NULL,\n      tags TEXT DEFAULT '[]',\n      created_at TEXT DEFAULT (datetime('now')),\n      updated_at TEXT DEFAULT (datetime('now'))\n    )\n  `);\n\n  return db;\n}\n\nexport function seedDatabase(db: Database.Database): void {\n  const insert = db.prepare(`\n    INSERT INTO notes (title, body, tags) VALUES (?, ?, ?)\n  `);\n\n  const notes = getSeedNotes();\n\n  const insertMany = db.transaction((items: { title: string; body: string; tags: string }[]) => {\n    for (const item of items) {\n      insert.run(item.title, item.body, item.tags);\n    }\n  });\n\n  insertMany(notes);\n}\n\nfunction getSeedNotes(): { title: string; body: string; tags: string }[] {\n  return [\n    {\n      title: 'Getting Started with TypeScript',\n      body: 'TypeScript is a typed superset of JavaScript that compiles to plain JavaScript. It adds optional static typing and class-based object-oriented programming to the language. TypeScript is designed for development of large applications and transcompiles to JavaScript.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'typescript', 'javascript']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Introduction to Python Programming',\n      body: 'Python is a high-level, interpreted programming language known for its simplicity and readability. It supports multiple programming paradigms including procedural, object-oriented, and functional programming. Python is widely used in web development, data science, and automation.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'python']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Understanding Database Indexing',\n      body: 'Database indexing is a data structure technique used to quickly locate and access data in a database. Indexes are created using columns that are frequently searched against. Without an index, the database must scan every row to find relevant data, which becomes slow for large tables.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['database', 'performance']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Homemade Pasta Recipe',\n      body: 'Making fresh pasta at home is surprisingly simple. You need flour, eggs, salt, and olive oil. Mix the ingredients to form a dough, knead for 10 minutes until smooth, rest for 30 minutes, then roll out and cut into your desired shape. Cook in boiling salted water for 2-3 minutes.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'recipes', 'italian']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Classic Chocolate Chip Cookies',\n      body: 'The perfect chocolate chip cookie requires butter, sugar, brown sugar, eggs, vanilla extract, flour, baking soda, salt, and chocolate chips. Cream the butter and sugars, add eggs and vanilla, mix in dry ingredients, fold in chocolate chips, and bake at 375°F for 9-11 minutes.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'recipes', 'baking']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Travel Guide: Tokyo Japan',\n      body: 'Tokyo is a fascinating blend of ultramodern and traditional. Visit the ancient Senso-ji temple, explore the bustling streets of Shibuya, enjoy fresh sushi at Tsukiji fish market, and experience the tranquility of Meiji Shrine. The best time to visit is during cherry blossom season in spring.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['travel', 'japan', 'asia']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Exploring Paris France',\n      body: 'Paris, the City of Light, offers world-class museums like the Louvre, iconic landmarks like the Eiffel Tower, charming neighborhoods like Montmartre, and exquisite cuisine. Stroll along the Seine, visit Notre-Dame Cathedral, and enjoy croissants at a sidewalk cafe.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['travel', 'france', 'europe']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Quantum Computing Basics',\n      body: 'Quantum computing leverages quantum mechanical phenomena like superposition and entanglement to process information. Unlike classical bits that are either 0 or 1, quantum bits (qubits) can exist in multiple states simultaneously. This enables quantum computers to solve certain problems exponentially faster.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['science', 'computing', 'physics']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'The Solar System Overview',\n      body: 'Our solar system consists of the Sun and everything that orbits it, including eight planets, dwarf planets, moons, asteroids, and comets. The inner planets (Mercury, Venus, Earth, Mars) are rocky, while the outer planets (Jupiter, Saturn, Uranus, Neptune) are gas or ice giants.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['science', 'astronomy', 'space']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Learning Guitar for Beginners',\n      body: 'Starting guitar requires patience and practice. Begin with basic open chords like G, C, D, E minor, and A minor. Practice transitioning between chords smoothly. Learn simple strumming patterns and work on finger strength. Playing just 15 minutes daily will show remarkable progress within weeks.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['music', 'guitar', 'learning']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'History of Jazz Music',\n      body: 'Jazz originated in the African-American communities of New Orleans in the late 19th and early 20th centuries. It blends elements of blues, ragtime, and European harmony. Key figures include Louis Armstrong, Duke Ellington, Charlie Parker, and Miles Davis. Jazz has evolved through many styles including swing, bebop, and fusion.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['music', 'history', 'jazz']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'React Hooks Deep Dive',\n      body: 'React Hooks allow you to use state and other React features without writing class components. useState manages local state, useEffect handles side effects, useContext accesses context, and useMemo optimizes performance. Custom hooks let you extract reusable stateful logic.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'react', 'javascript']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Docker Container Essentials',\n      body: 'Docker containers package applications with their dependencies into standardized units for development, shipment, and deployment. Containers are lightweight, portable, and consistent across environments. Key concepts include images, containers, volumes, networks, and docker-compose for multi-container applications.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'devops', 'docker']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Mediterranean Diet Benefits',\n      body: 'The Mediterranean diet emphasizes fruits, vegetables, whole grains, legumes, nuts, and olive oil. It includes moderate amounts of fish, poultry, and dairy, with limited red meat. Studies show it reduces risk of heart disease, stroke, type 2 diabetes, and cognitive decline.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['health', 'nutrition', 'diet']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Yoga for Stress Relief',\n      body: 'Yoga combines physical postures, breathing exercises, and meditation to promote relaxation and reduce stress. Regular practice improves flexibility, strength, and mental clarity. Beginner-friendly poses include child pose, downward dog, warrior I and II, and tree pose.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['health', 'fitness', 'yoga']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Machine Learning Fundamentals',\n      body: 'Machine learning is a subset of artificial intelligence where algorithms learn patterns from data without being explicitly programmed. Key types include supervised learning (classification, regression), unsupervised learning (clustering), and reinforcement learning. Popular frameworks include TensorFlow, PyTorch, and scikit-learn.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'ai', 'machine-learning']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Backpacking Through Southeast Asia',\n      body: 'Southeast Asia offers incredible backpacking experiences on a budget. Visit ancient temples in Cambodia, pristine beaches in Thailand, rice terraces in Vietnam, and vibrant cities in Malaysia. Budget around $30-50 per day for accommodation, food, and transport.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['travel', 'asia', 'backpacking']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Sourdough Bread Baking Guide',\n      body: 'Sourdough bread requires a mature starter, flour, water, and salt. The process involves mixing, autolyse, bulk fermentation with stretch and folds, shaping, cold retard overnight, and baking in a Dutch oven. The natural fermentation creates complex flavors and better digestibility.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'baking', 'bread']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Introduction to Rust Programming',\n      body: 'Rust is a systems programming language focused on safety, speed, and concurrency. Its ownership system prevents null pointer dereferences, dangling pointers, and data races at compile time. Rust is ideal for performance-critical applications, web assembly, and embedded systems.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'rust', 'systems']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Climate Change and Renewable Energy',\n      body: 'Renewable energy sources like solar, wind, hydroelectric, and geothermal are essential for combating climate change. Solar panel costs have dropped 89% since 2010. Wind energy is the fastest-growing power source globally. Transitioning to renewables can significantly reduce greenhouse gas emissions.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['science', 'environment', 'energy']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Photography Composition Techniques',\n      body: 'Great photography relies on strong composition. The rule of thirds places subjects at grid intersections. Leading lines guide the viewer eye. Framing uses natural elements to surround the subject. Symmetry creates balance. Negative space emphasizes the main subject by leaving empty areas.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['photography', 'art', 'techniques']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'GraphQL vs REST API Design',\n      body: 'GraphQL lets clients request exactly the data they need in a single query, reducing over-fetching and under-fetching common with REST. REST uses multiple endpoints with fixed data structures. GraphQL has a single endpoint with a flexible query language. Both have tradeoffs in caching, complexity, and tooling.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'api', 'web']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'The Art of French Cooking',\n      body: 'French cuisine is built on foundational techniques: the five mother sauces (bechamel, veloute, espagnole, hollandaise, tomato), proper knife skills, stock making, and mastering heat control. Classic dishes include coq au vin, beef bourguignon, ratatouille, and creme brulee.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['cooking', 'french', 'techniques']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Hiking the Appalachian Trail',\n      body: 'The Appalachian Trail stretches 2,190 miles from Georgia to Maine through 14 states. Thru-hiking takes 5-7 months. Section hiking is popular for those with less time. Essential gear includes a quality backpack, lightweight tent, sleeping bag, water filter, and proper hiking boots.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['travel', 'hiking', 'outdoors']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Kubernetes Orchestration Guide',\n      body: 'Kubernetes automates deployment, scaling, and management of containerized applications. Key concepts include pods, services, deployments, namespaces, and ingress controllers. Kubernetes provides self-healing, horizontal scaling, rolling updates, and service discovery out of the box.',\n      tags: JSON.stringify(['programming', 'devops', 'kubernetes']),\n    },\n    {\n      title: 'Classical Music Appreciation',\n      body: 'Classical music spans centuries from Bach and Handel